67
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:10,260
Here comes the Crown Prince.

68
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:13,660
Your Highness.

69
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:14,460
Your Highness!

70
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:20,180
Your Highness,

71
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:21,900
Mei Yushan and her maid

72
00:03:21,980 --> 00:03:23,300
escaped from the brig secretly,

73
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:24,420
which violates the palace rules.

74
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,860
I beg Your Highness to punish them.

75
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:28,180
They'd better be flogged eighty times.

76
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:29,780
What do you mean by escaping?

77
00:03:29,780 --> 00:03:31,340
I went out with the Crown Prince
to handle affairs.

78
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:32,380
Must I tell you about it?

79
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:34,260
You don't have to tell us.

80
00:03:34,260 --> 00:03:36,620
But did you tell Her Majesty about it?

81
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:39,380
Put me down.

82
00:03:45,940 --> 00:03:46,220
Of course,

83
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:48,140
