would be reported to Her Majesty.

84
00:03:48,380 --> 00:03:49,940
But Miss Zhuang refuses to let it go.

85
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:52,300
Is it because you want
to drive a wedge between them?

86
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:53,180
You...

87
00:03:54,660 --> 00:03:55,900
Do I have to repeat

88
00:03:56,580 --> 00:03:58,140
what they just said?

89
00:03:58,580 --> 00:03:59,020
But...

90
00:03:59,020 --> 00:03:59,940
I dare not.

91
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:14,220
Are you okay?

92
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:17,260
