catching the chicken.

106
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:36,220
I haven't eaten anything today, either.

107
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:39,420
And she wouldn't allow me
to do anything.

108
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:44,180
Here I come.

109
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:45,300
I can stew the chicken now.

110
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:54,380
What are you doing?

111
00:05:54,740 --> 00:05:55,700
Stewing the chicken with herbs.

112
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:57,860
It is still alive.

113
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:59,420
You need to kill it and get it plucked.

114
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:01,940
