How do I do that?

115
00:06:01,940 --> 00:06:02,580
Nanbei.

116
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:04,060
Get me a towel.

117
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:05,100
I'll help Douzi wash up.

118
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:07,100
Let me do it for her.

119
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:08,300
It is improper for men and women
to touch each other.

120
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:18,700
Nanbei.

121
00:06:19,020 --> 00:06:20,180
Hurry to prepare a carriage.

122
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:21,860
We'll take Douzi back
to the Eastern Palace for her to rest.

123
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:23,260
- Thank you, Your Highness... - Yes.

124
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:24,260
- But if Douzi...
- Ask Eunuch Song...

125
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:25,540
- goes with you...
- to clean this place up.

126
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:27,340
to the Eastern Palace,
she'll be criticized again.

127
00:06:27,340 --> 00:06:29,100
I remember, in The Book of Songs,

128
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,980
it is said that one must always
restrain oneself even when in love.

129
00:06:30,980 --> 00:06:32,420
It is human nature
to fall in love with others.

130
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:33,250
But restraining oneself
is the indoctrination

131
00:06:33,250 --> 00:06:34,020
of the deceased emperors in former times

132
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:35,140
Moreover, Confucius and Mencius
also advocated

133
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:36,100
that it is improper for men and women
to touch each other.

134
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,100
Even if you are in love,

135
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:38,220
