136
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:39,060
Your Highness.

137
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:40,620
Your Highness?

138
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:47,300
Now the Emperor is ill.

139
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:49,540
And something tricky
happened to the Crown Prince.

140
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:52,220
