141
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:56,140
That Shen Yu
is a courtier and an official,

142
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:58,180
yet he failed
to protect the Crown Prince.

143
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:01,860
I think that's the end of his career.

144
00:07:03,980 --> 00:07:04,740
Your Majesty.

145
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,340
Don't be mad.

146
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,060
Have some ginseng soup.

147
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:22,100
You've served me for years,
how can't you tell the difference

148
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:24,940
between the wild ginseng
and the western ginseng?

149
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:26,820
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

150
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,820
This morning I went
to the Imperial Household Department.

151
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:30,420
But the head of the department said,

152
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:33,500
