all the supplements.

153
00:07:33,540 --> 00:07:34,980
Especially wild ginseng.

154
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:36,780
Not a single one left.

155
00:07:38,980 --> 00:07:40,860
It's okay if they were all eaten
by the Crown Prince.

156
00:07:42,220 --> 00:07:42,860
It's good.

157
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:49,740
Ever since the Grand Tutor said
Miss Mei was weak,

158
