You stupid girl.

546
00:26:01,980 --> 00:26:03,660
I already told you

547
00:26:03,660 --> 00:26:04,620
when you go out,
you need to check the weather

548
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:06,100
and mind your step.

549
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:07,540
You have no manners.

550
00:26:11,060 --> 00:26:12,980
Do you also think I have no manners?

551
00:26:16,660 --> 00:26:18,020
Has your injury recovered?

552
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:20,380
Almost. I'm leaving.

553
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:21,100
Stop.

554
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:23,860
Without His Highness's permission,

555
00:26:23,860 --> 00:26:25,180
you can't go anywhere.

556
00:26:26,740 --> 00:26:27,820
Moreover,

557
00:26:28,060 --> 00:26:31,220
I haven't diagnosed you yet.

558
00:26:31,220 --> 00:26:32,620
I'm really healed.

559
00:26:32,620 --> 00:26:33,380
I'll show you.

560
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:35,580
- Stop it.
- I can even run.

561
00:26:35,580 --> 00:26:37,380
- I can spin around.
- Oh, please no.

562
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:39,340
- Injured bones need months to heal.
- I can also jump.

563
00:26:39,340 --> 00:26:41,460
I can even jump now.

564
00:26:41,460 --> 00:26:42,420
Be careful.

565
00:26:45,220 --> 00:26:46,540
My herbs.

566
00:27:11,980 --> 00:27:13,660
Mr. Bai is so gentle.

567
00:27:15,340 --> 00:27:16,540
Little Diviner?

568
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:19,500
Did that scare you?

569
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:21,780
Thank you for saving me, Little Diviner.

570
00:27:23,420 --> 00:27:24,700
I have a feeling right now

571
00:27:24,700 --> 00:27:26,340
that His Highness is coming armed

572
00:27:26,340 --> 00:27:27,700
with burning anger.

573
00:27:40,820 --> 00:27:41,620
How are your wounds?

574
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:43,180
Almost healed.

575
00:27:43,580 --> 00:27:44,100
Come on.

576
00:27:45,820 --> 00:27:47,500
His Highness is here.

577
00:27:52,500 --> 00:27:53,100
Your Highness.

578
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:53,980
Your Highness.

579
00:27:57,140 --> 00:27:57,980
What are you waiting for?

580
00:27:58,260 --> 00:27:59,860
Invite Mr. Bai in for a cup of tea.

581
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:00,860
Yes.

582
00:28:06,020 --> 00:28:07,860
You're not healed, yet you have
the energy to tear the house down?

583
00:28:07,980 --> 00:28:09,380
I'm almost healed.

584
00:28:09,780 --> 00:28:10,740
I don't think so.

585
00:28:11,460 --> 00:28:12,780
Why else would you fall so suddenly?

586
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:16,460
It's... It's because the Grand Tutor

587
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:19,580
insisted that I had not recovered.

588
00:28:25,060 --> 00:28:25,580
Patients...

589
00:28:25,580 --> 00:28:26,140
So handsome.

590
00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:27,660
should receive special treatment.

591
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:28,260
I...

592
00:28:29,020 --> 00:28:29,940
Just put me down.

593
00:28:29,940 --> 00:28:30,780
I want to hold you.

594
00:28:33,580 --> 00:28:34,580
Oh no.

595
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:36,380
This is so embarrassing.

596
00:28:43,660 --> 00:28:44,700
I'll take my leave then.

597
00:28:44,700 --> 00:28:45,540
I'll come another day.

598
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:46,220
Zuo,

599
00:28:47,780 --> 00:28:49,780
brew the fine Jinjunmei black tea
that just arrived

600
00:28:50,180 --> 00:28:51,420
for Mr. Bai.

601
00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:52,340
Yes.

602
00:28:57,300 --> 00:28:58,500
I'm clearly not reconciled to it.

603
00:28:59,460 --> 00:29:01,500
I envy him for being able

604
00:29:01,660 --> 00:29:03,020
to express his feelings freely.

605
00:29:04,140 --> 00:29:05,580
But there is a sense of relief.

606
00:29:06,540 --> 00:29:07,820
If he really falls in love

607
00:29:08,340 --> 00:29:09,500
with Douzi,

608
00:29:10,220 --> 00:29:11,780
the prophecy about Shengdong's Princess

609
00:29:12,060 --> 00:29:13,340
will be proved wrong.

610
00:29:14,100 --> 00:29:16,300
If His Highness and Douzi get married,

611
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:19,020
what I foresaw

612
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:21,260
will be totally wrong.

613
00:29:29,500 --> 00:29:30,340
Harder.

614
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:36,620
Yeah, keep him down.

615
00:29:36,620 --> 00:29:39,550
[Wuer Martial Arts]

616
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,780
Back in Shengdong,

617
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:52,260
General Wang, have you heard

618
00:29:52,260 --> 00:29:53,460
of the Moon Spirit Pearl?

619
00:29:54,820 --> 00:29:55,620
For example,

620
00:29:56,420 --> 00:29:57,980
can it make two people
switch their bodies?

621
00:30:02,100 --> 00:30:04,700
I know it sounds crazy.

622
00:30:05,260 --> 00:30:06,900
I heard it when I was a kid.

623
00:30:07,580 --> 00:30:08,780
But it was so long ago
that I couldn't remember,

624
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:10,900
so I specially came to you
for confirmation.

625
00:30:12,660 --> 00:30:13,900
Hearing you talk about it,

626
00:30:14,100 --> 00:30:15,660
I do remember one thing.

627
00:30:16,140 --> 00:30:17,620
About forty years ago,

628
00:30:18,620 --> 00:30:20,300
our emperor then
gave the Moon Spirit Pearl

629
00:30:20,300 --> 00:30:21,620
to his son-in-law.

630
00:30:22,140 --> 00:30:23,900
His son-in-law loved
the princess very much.

631
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:26,260
So he made her a headdress
with the pearl.

632
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:30,780
He took the Moon Spirit Pearl

633
00:30:30,900 --> 00:30:32,820
to find the famous jeweler
to make the headdress for her.

634
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:34,700
It didn't take long

635
00:30:35,780 --> 00:30:37,980
before the emperor's son-in-law's
temperament changed dramatically.

636
00:30:38,220 --> 00:30:39,660
He was as mad as a hatter.

637
00:30:40,420 --> 00:30:41,500
The jeweler
was keeping crying out his grievances,

638
00:30:42,140 --> 00:30:44,900
saying that he was the emperor's
son-in-law.

639
00:30:44,980 --> 00:30:46,500
People called him a lunatic.

640
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:51,060
Looks like I was right.

641
00:30:52,100 --> 00:30:52,860
However,

642
00:30:53,140 --> 00:30:54,900
I'm not sure if it had anything to do

643
00:30:55,140 --> 00:30:56,180
with the Moon Spirit Pearl.

644
00:30:58,100 --> 00:30:59,100
My Princess,

645
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:00,700
I finally found you.

646
00:31:12,580 --> 00:31:13,500
Why are you leaving?

647
00:31:14,540 --> 00:31:16,380
To stop those people
from gossiping behind our backs.

648
00:31:18,260 --> 00:31:19,580
All they can do is gossip.

649
00:31:20,980 --> 00:31:21,420
If you leave,

650
00:31:21,420 --> 00:31:23,340
you give those people
exactly what they want.

651
00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:31,460
I'm using a fake identity now.

652
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:32,740
They all say I don't deserve you.

653
00:31:32,900 --> 00:31:34,020
Then if they find out

654
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:36,220
that I'm a thief
who grew up in an alley,

655
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:36,900
won't they even...

656
00:31:36,900 --> 00:31:37,940
I don't care about any of that.

657
00:31:37,940 --> 00:31:39,180
Why do you care?

658
00:31:40,820 --> 00:31:42,020
They're right.

659
00:31:42,500 --> 00:31:44,420
I have no manners.

660
00:31:45,020 --> 00:31:46,540
I don't deserve you.

661
00:31:48,060 --> 00:31:48,660
Little Master.

662
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:51,580
Nonsense.

663
00:31:59,300 --> 00:32:00,540
You are not inferior to anyone.

664
00:32:00,940 --> 00:32:01,620
As for the manners,

665
00:32:01,620 --> 00:32:02,980
you can learn them gradually.

666
00:32:05,740 --> 00:32:07,460
Do you also think I have no manners,

667
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:08,780
and I need to learn about them?

668
00:32:11,620 --> 00:32:12,340
Let go.

669
00:32:13,380 --> 00:32:14,540
That's not what I meant.

670
00:32:15,460 --> 00:32:16,860
As for the manners,
if you don't like it,

671
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:17,820
you don't have to learn.

672
00:32:18,980 --> 00:32:20,060
I'm someone

673
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:21,860
who was born

674
00:32:21,860 --> 00:32:23,780
with a wild and free soul.

675
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:25,020
I can't learn those manners.

676
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:28,540
Besides, I'm just a civilian.

677
00:32:28,980 --> 00:32:30,100
I'm just like Little Diviner,

678
00:32:30,540 --> 00:32:33,060
who came to the palace by accident.

679
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:36,020
As for you, Your Highness,

680
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:37,940
I never want to be with you.

681
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:40,340
I know don't deserve you.

682
00:32:47,580 --> 00:32:48,700
What do you mean by that?

683
00:32:51,780 --> 00:32:53,380
Are you mad at me or...

684
00:32:53,660 --> 00:32:54,260
I...

685
00:32:56,300 --> 00:32:58,420
I'm not mad at you.

686
00:32:59,860 --> 00:33:04,900
I... I want to go back
to the Guixiu Pavilion.

687
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:23,100
See her back.

688
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:30,700
Yes.

689
00:33:32,740 --> 00:33:35,900
I'm actually mad at myself.

690
00:33:45,380 --> 00:33:48,180
Learning without thinking is labor lost.

691
00:33:48,340 --> 00:33:50,780
Thinking without learning is idle.

692
00:33:51,380 --> 00:33:53,820
When seeing a worthy person,
think of following in his footsteps.

693
00:33:53,980 --> 00:33:57,460
When seeing the unwise ones,
examine yourself internally.

694
00:33:58,180 --> 00:34:01,820
You can always learn from others.

695
00:34:02,300 --> 00:34:05,020
Choose the good and follow them,

696
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:09,380
and correct those that are not good.

697
00:34:11,580 --> 00:34:13,660
I'm talking to you.
When will you give it back?

698
00:34:13,660 --> 00:34:16,020
Stop pestering me.

699
00:34:16,740 --> 00:34:17,380
I'll give you.

700
00:34:17,380 --> 00:34:18,140
How long has it been?

701
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:19,180
What are you talking about?

702
00:34:19,180 --> 00:34:20,220
No.

703
00:34:20,980 --> 00:34:22,260
Shuo, hurry up.

704
00:34:23,460 --> 00:34:25,020
I've got things to do.
Get out of my way.

705
00:34:25,220 --> 00:34:26,060
Come here.

706
00:34:26,220 --> 00:34:28,460
You're cheating again.

707
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:29,300
Give it back to me.

708
00:34:29,300 --> 00:34:30,460
Didn't I tell you not to lend it to him?

709
00:34:30,500 --> 00:34:31,860
Get it back or you'll never get it.

710
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:33,660
- Give it back.
- No, I won't.

711
00:34:33,660 --> 00:34:34,780
Don't run.

712
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:36,540
Give me.

713
00:34:39,180 --> 00:34:40,300
Su Ruomei.

714
00:34:41,300 --> 00:34:44,820
♪We walk together on bustling streets♪

715
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:45,780
Huang Yuanyuan.

716
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:49,460
♪My heart leans
towards your warm embrace♪

717
00:34:49,460 --> 00:34:50,420
Second Prince.

718
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:55,420
♪We're both kites reclaimed
from the edge of the sky♪

719
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:56,540
Mei Yushan.

720
00:34:57,140 --> 00:34:58,140
Mei Yushan?

721
00:34:58,140 --> 00:35:01,060
♪If it's an unfathomable fate,
let me do it again♪

722
00:35:01,060 --> 00:35:02,540
Mei Yushan.

723
00:35:03,450 --> 00:35:09,440
♪We're both misunderstood,
yet we accept it willingly♪

724
00:35:09,860 --> 00:35:15,020
♪Step forth boldly and join me
without asking where we're heading♪

725
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:15,780
Give it to me.

726
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:43,020
Mei Yushan hasn't come to the Academy
for several days.

727
00:35:43,380 --> 00:35:44,420
Don't you know about that?

728
00:35:45,940 --> 00:35:46,940
I do.

729
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:48,180
You do?

730
00:35:53,820 --> 00:35:55,340
You're the steward
of the Guixiu Pavilion.

731
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:56,620
But you indulged her
and failed your duty.

732
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:59,260
I do not understand.

733
00:36:00,460 --> 00:36:02,340
Do we pay you for nothing?

734
00:36:03,420 --> 00:36:05,300
Your Highness, Miss Mei was recently

735
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:07,140
summoned to the Huacai Hall
by Her Majesty

736
00:36:07,140 --> 00:36:08,500
to learn manners.

737
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:10,580
What manners?

738
00:36:13,100 --> 00:36:15,660
I'm sure Her Majesty
can read Your Highness's mind.

739
00:36:15,980 --> 00:36:17,180
I think

740
00:36:17,620 --> 00:36:19,540
this is to prepare for your marriage.

741
00:36:31,220 --> 00:36:31,980
You may leave.

742
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:34,380
I'll take my leave then.

743
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:51,310
♪It's your mesmerizing glance♪

744
00:36:51,630 --> 00:36:54,900
♪Freezing the gentle breeze
of the mundane world♪

745
00:36:54,960 --> 00:37:00,530
♪Your gentle call awakens me
from my unfinished dreams♪

746
00:37:00,530 --> 00:37:04,180
♪It's hard to convey my love for you
when fighting for the homeland♪

747
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:07,700
♪Our destined encounter♪

748
00:37:07,700 --> 00:37:12,560
♪I am meant to accompany you
on this journey♪

749
00:37:13,010 --> 00:37:16,080
♪Wishing for a bit more♪

750
00:37:16,210 --> 00:37:19,790
♪So love feels even more real♪

751
00:37:19,790 --> 00:37:25,430
♪You and I, each completing the other,
year after year♪

752
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:28,450
♪Accompany me to explore the world♪

753
00:37:28,450 --> 00:37:32,100
♪We walk together on bustling streets♪

754
00:37:32,290 --> 00:37:37,470
♪My heart leans
towards your warm embrace♪

755
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:44,450
♪We're both kites reclaimed
from the edge of the sky♪

756
00:37:44,580 --> 00:37:50,030
♪If it's an unfathomable fate,
let me do it again♪

757
00:37:50,030 --> 00:37:56,490
♪We're both misunderstood,
yet we accept it willingly♪

758
00:37:56,940 --> 00:38:05,770
♪Step forth boldly and join me
without asking where we're heading♪
